mapper.select: SELECT , DbT5207."remban" AS "状況連番", DbT5207."serviceJokyo" AS "状況" FROM "${csvTempTableName}" AS "CsvTempTable" LEFT JOIN rgdb."DbT5207NinteichosahyoServiceJokyo" AS DbT5207 ON DbT5207."shinseishoKanriNo" :: text = "CsvTempTable"."申請書管理番号" AND DbT5207."ninteichosaRirekiNo" :: text = "CsvTempTable"."認定調査依頼履歴番号" AND DbT5207."koroshoIfShikibetsuCode" :: text = "CsvTempTable"."厚労省IF識別コード" ORDER BY "申請書管理番号", "状況連番"

SELECT , DbT5208."remban" AS "状況フラグ連番", DbT5208."serviceJokyoFlag" AS "状況フラグ" FROM "${csvTempTableName}" AS "CsvTempTable" LEFT JOIN rgdb."DbT5208NinteichosahyoServiceJokyoFlag" AS DbT5208 ON DbT5208."shinseishoKanriNo" :: text = "CsvTempTable"."申請書管理番号" AND DbT5208."ninteichosaRirekiNo" :: text = "CsvTempTable"."認定調査依頼履歴番号" AND DbT5208."koroshoIfShikibetsuCode" :: text = "CsvTempTable"."厚労省IF識別コード" ORDER BY "申請書管理番号", "状況フラグ連番"

SELECT , DbT5209."remban" AS "記入項目連番", regexp_replace(DbT5209."serviceJokyoKinyu",E'(\r\n|\r|\n|\t)','','g') AS "状況記入" FROM "${csvTempTableName}" AS "CsvTempTable" LEFT JOIN rgdb."DbT5209NinteichosahyoKinyuItem" AS DbT5209 ON DbT5209."shinseishoKanriNo" :: text = "CsvTempTable"."申請書管理番号" AND DbT5209."ninteichosaRirekiNo" :: text = "CsvTempTable"."認定調査依頼履歴番号" AND DbT5209."koroshoIfShikibetsuCode" :: text = "CsvTempTable"."厚労省IF識別コード" ORDER BY "申請書管理番号", "記入項目連番"

SELECT , DbT5210."remban" AS "施設利用連番", DbT5210."shisetsuRiyoFlag" AS "施設利用フラグ" FROM "${csvTempTableName}" AS "CsvTempTable" LEFT JOIN rgdb."DbT5210NinteichosahyoShisetsuRiyo"AS DbT5210 ON DbT5210."shinseishoKanriNo" :: text = "CsvTempTable"."申請書管理番号" AND DbT5210."ninteichosaRirekiNo" :: text = "CsvTempTable"."認定調査依頼履歴番号" AND DbT5210."koroshoIfShikibetsuCode" :: text = "CsvTempTable"."厚労省IF識別コード" ORDER BY "申請書管理番号", "施設利用連番"

SELECT , DbT5211."remban" AS "調査項目連番", DbT5211."researchItem" AS "調査項目" FROM "${csvTempTableName}" AS "CsvTempTable" LEFT JOIN rgdb."DbT5211NinteichosahyoChosaItem"AS DbT5211 ON DbT5211."shinseishoKanriNo" :: text = "CsvTempTable"."申請書管理番号" AND DbT5211."ninteichosaRirekiNo" :: text = "CsvTempTable"."認定調査依頼履歴番号" AND DbT5211."koroshoIfShikibetsuCode" :: text = "CsvTempTable"."厚労省IF識別コード" ORDER BY "申請書管理番号", "調査項目連番"

SELECT ,
FROM "${csvTempTableName}" AS "CsvTempTable" LEFT JOIN "${csvTempTableNameZenkai}" AS "CsvTempTableZenkai" ON "CsvTempTable".申請書管理番号 = "CsvTempTableZenkai".前回申請書管理番号
